title: ~ 15 mins to Downtown - New 1bd - 1 month free - Luxury pool & Gym
posting_body: 💰 Listed price is factoring in the special of 1 month free over a 13-month lease term.
🏠 This is a very unique 1bd floor-plan.
The living room and kitchen offer a ton of space to customize however you like.
Next to the entry is a little nook offering enough space for a small dining table.
🔥 1 month free Special is for August Move-ins.
👌🏼 This community is only 10 miles to the heart of  Austin, mins to shopping & dining, and easy access to Highway 35.
☀ With each unit you get w/dryer included and parking included.
This community includes common workspaces, community areas with pool table, massive gym, and nice infinity pool.
😄 I'm a licensed Apartment locator and get paid by the properties so my service is 100% free.
I have been doing this job for over 5 years.
I love what I do and my goal is to make your apartment search as easy and smooth as possible.
Don't hesitate to text or call me and use my knowledge of Austin's market to assure you get a great deal on your next apartment.
